itochu techno-solutions corp (4739) Details


			ITOCHU Techno-Solutions Corporation provides various IT services primarily in Japan. It engages in the sale, maintenance, and support of computers and network systems; provision of operation and management services of IT systems, infrastructure operation and management services, business and application operation and management services, software development services, and satellite communications and broadcasting operation services; and sale of network and security-related equipment, storage devices, and packaged software, as well as provision of related services. The company also offers hardware for the pharmaceutical, chemical, and food product industries; software sales and support, and agency services; building facility operations management activities for computer centers; and plans, produces, and maintains Web content, as well as plans and produces advertising materials. In addition, it is involved in the provision of contact center operations, helpdesk services, and IT training, as well as planning and implementation of IT training; system development, maintenance, operation, and IT consulting; and massaging, office cleaning, and washing service for clothes dirty with office works, and light work that accompanies agriculture, etc. Further, the company offers software development, information processing, and information services related to science and engineering; exports IT products; and resells hardware and software. It serves various industries, such as telecommunication, finance, distribution, manufacturing, education and public sector, and science and engineering. The company was founded in 1972 and is headquartered in Tokyo, Japan. ITOCHU Techno-Solutions Corporation is a subsidiary of ITOCHU Corporation.
  			

