					Full Description



		ITOCHU Techno-Solutions Corporation is a company mainly engaged in the provision and maintenance of computer network systems, the customized development of software, the provision of data centre services and support. Information Communications segment, Financial and Social Infrastructure segment, Enterprise segment and Distribution segment are engaged in integrated proposal and sales activities, including consulting, system design and construction, maintenance and operation. Cloud Platform segment is engaged in joint proposal and procurement focusing on information technology (IT) infrastructure outsourcing. Maintenance and Operation Service segment is engaged in joint proposal and procurement focusing on maintenance and operation service. Others segment is engaged in product sourcing activities. As of March 31, 2014, the Company had 13 consolidated subsidiaries and five associated companies.
» Full Overview of ITTOY.PK







